    "body": "Enables all modules by default, and tests the disabling of each module separately (respecting the dependency chain). This simplifies the configuration of modules in CI and extends the test coverage.\r\n\r\nThe extended coverage is proven by exposing pre-existing issues fixed in #1837 and #1839.",
